HAVEN / REGAL Shoe & Co. Tyrolean GORE-TEX.

This modern interpretation of the classic Tyrolean silhouette features a multi-textured cowhide upper—engineered to GORE-TEX® brand standards for all-weather comfort.

Goodyear welt construction offers durability and water resistance, while a Vibram® MegaGrip outsole delivers traction across wet urban surfaces and natural terrain.

Available Friday, May 30th online and in stores.
